Package: r4sda
Type: Package
Title: Collection of functions to produce descriptives analysis of secondary data and large scale assessments studies
Version: 0.1.0
Author: dacarras
Maintainer: The package maintainer <dacarras@uc.cl>
Description: This is collection of functions, mostly wrappers, that I used very often for secondary data analysis. Most of these secondary data anaysis are done with large scale assessment or national data records in education, or large sample surveys. These functions includes generating scores, table frequencies, codebooks, and other common objects.
Imports: dplyr, tidyr, haven, labelled, tibble, lme4, broom.mixed, stringr, rlang, survey, tools, skimr, stats, moments
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
